                        is mentioned as the scribe in the concluding supplication (<locus target="#105rb">105rb</locus>).
 
                       The Ms. is written in the same hand as <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESktm008">KTM-008</ref>.<date notBefore="1925" notAfter="1975">Mid 20th century</date>

